Nigeria to Offer 76.73 Billion Naira of T-Bills on April 28

-- B y   V i n c e n t   N w a n m a
-- 
2011-04-21T10:16:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-21/nigeria-to-offer-76-73-billion-naira-of-t-bills-on-april-28.html
Nigeria will offer 76.73 billion
naira ($496 million) of Treasury bills in an auction on April
28, the central bank said today.  The Abuja-based  Central Bank of Nigeria  will offer 91- and
182-day bills, according to an advertisement published in the
 Guardian newspaper .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vincent Nwanma in Lagos at 
 vnwanma@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net .
